Articles.Content:
Hello guys, so I've been playing KSP for a while now, and i thought it would be nice if i shared one of my Spacecraft Designs, it's very simple, 4 Lv-N engines, 7725 units of liquid fuel, a standard MK3 cargo-bay for the Dolphin Launcher.

 

The Craft has 6300 Delta-V (4500 with the lander) and the Dolphin has 2500 Delta V.

 

 

P.S i have no idea how to post download links, and sorry for bad english, it's not my native language.
